##Product##
Request Type    api                            description
  GET           api/products  -> fetch all products
  GET           api/products/{product_id} -> find a product by product id
  GET           api/products/{product_name} -> find a product by name
  POST          api/products                -> create a product
  PUT           api/products/{product_id} -> update a product by product id
**PUT           api/products               -> update a product
  DELETE        api/products/{product_id} -> delete a product
  POST          api/search                 -> search e product
